<em>展开全文</em>
</a>
</section>
</div>
<div class="hidden-content control-hide">
<p class="ql-align-center">﹀</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20200818/246fcb5f06e645b29cc6836bbb6be8eb.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>藏八露二的柜子</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">如果想来点时尚感，</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">不如康康下面这款藏八露二的柜子。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">更多颜色的加入使柜子看起来更吸睛，</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">摆在家中很有活力。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">﹀</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20200818/6904949eeca94bfc851ad42eeec181fb.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>藤编柜</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">除了比较常见的实木对开门柜子，</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">藤编的柜门，也是我非常喜欢的一款！</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">搭配上绿植，则既显自然之感。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">﹀</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20200818/289108669eef41c5be5ccf9f9aba06d6.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>金属柜</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">和木质柜子不同，</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">白色的金属柜子则具有很强的现代感，</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">非常适合装修风格简约，喜用浅色，</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">款式简单大方家居的家庭。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">﹀</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20200818/44a864d732c34ce5936cf48bcd07bd3a.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>高脚柜</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">同样值得一提的还有高脚柜，</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">而且高脚柜和床头位置绝配。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">本就满当当的卧室，采用高脚柜后会瞬间显轻便，</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">而且底部不积灰，好清洁。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">﹀</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20200818/4654f20c78024de49a577f2a96ad4dc9.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>矮柜的位置</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">矮柜虽然收纳能力不足顶天立地柜，</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">但其使用位置也十分广泛。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">餐边柜</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">﹀</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20200818/756cc74dc7c1486f9f7d3942f0b2287b.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">靠墙摆放</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">﹀</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20200818/9cf704c30dd44bff8d1ec49bdaccdb7a.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">窗户下</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">﹀</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20200818/27bbfcf0c6304c57b5f5c7fd9eee2c75.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">玄关位置</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">﹀</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20200818/00552eac75634c79bdf6d3e702be55a9.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>